.DS_Store

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Jupyter
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Data files (all in data/ — lives in Google Drive, never in GitHub)
data/

# Output
plots/

# Experiment outputs live in Google Drive, NOT GitHub.
# Whitelist only small text/config artifacts that aid reproducibility.
experiments/**
!experiments/**/
!experiments/**/README.md
!experiments/**/prereg.json
!experiments/**/hp_grid.json
!experiments/**/news_edge_source_schema.md
!experiments/README.md

# Artifacts: logs + large run outputs live in Google Drive.
# Whitelist Codex / reviewer text reports — they document the review trail.
artifacts/**
!artifacts/**/
!artifacts/README.md
!artifacts/reviews/
!artifacts/reviews/**
# Story A E6 + LOFO + diagnostic — small text/JSON artifacts supporting paper §Results
!artifacts/storya_e6_dm_spa/*.json
!artifacts/storya_e6_dm_spa/*.csv
!artifacts/storya_e6_dm_spa/*.md
!artifacts/plan_aaa_t1_diagnostic/*.csv
!artifacts/plan_aaa_t1_diagnostic/*.md
!artifacts/storya_e6_edge_ablation/*.csv
!artifacts/storya_e6_edge_ablation/*.md

# Claude Code — whitelist shareable team infrastructure, ignore everything else by default.
# Previously (pre-2026-04-23) blanket-ignored `.claude/`, which broke Rule 9 infra shipping.
# Intermediate fix (2026-04-23 earlier) only blocked settings files, which silently tracked
# any future Claude-Code-generated cache / log / session state.
# Final fix: deny-all-then-allow pattern — safe against future Claude Code files.
.claude/*
!.claude/rules/
!.claude/rules/**
!.claude/commands/
!.claude/commands/**
!.claude/agents/
!.claude/agents/**

# Colab run results
colab result/

# API keys (NEVER commit)
openrouter_key.txt
api_key*.txt
.env
*.key
